= Target =
Have fix address, included with change of internet provider, or have multiple internet connexion. This include for other service than http, like: mail (pop, smtp), irc, xmpp, ... Have access to site web via the normal web thanks to inproxy (XXXXXX.b32.i2p.us), and less sensible to dns or routing security leak.

